74 /*========== Extern Function Implementations ================================*/
75 extern void SE_InitializeSoc(bool ccPresent, uint8_t stringNumber) {
76  FAS_ASSERT(stringNumber < BS_NR_OF_STRINGS);
77  SE_InitializeStateOfCharge(&se_tableSocAndSoeEstimation, ccPresent, stringNumber);
78  DATA_WRITE_DATA(&se_tableSocAndSoeEstimation);
79 }
80 
81 extern void SE_InitializeSoe(bool ec_present, uint8_t stringNumber) {
82  FAS_ASSERT(stringNumber < BS_NR_OF_STRINGS);
83  SE_InitializeStateOfEnergy(&se_tableSocAndSoeEstimation, ec_present, stringNumber);
84  DATA_WRITE_DATA(&se_tableSocAndSoeEstimation);
85 }
86 
87 extern void SE_InitializeSoh(uint8_t stringNumber) {
88  FAS_ASSERT(stringNumber < BS_NR_OF_STRINGS);
89  SE_InitializeStateOfHealth(&se_tableSocAndSoeEstimation, stringNumber);
90  DATA_WRITE_DATA(&se_tableSocAndSoeEstimation);
91 }
92 
93 extern void SE_RunStateEstimations(void) {
94  SE_CalculateStateOfCharge(&se_tableSocAndSoeEstimation);
95  SE_CalculateStateOfEnergy(&se_tableSocAndSoeEstimation);
96  SE_CalculateStateOfHealth(&se_tableSocAndSoeEstimation);
97 
98  DATA_WRITE_DATA(&se_tableSocAndSoeEstimation);
99 }
